title: Happy Birthday Kobi
content:
Happy birthday to my amazing Kobi.
 You've just turned 6 and every day you've been in my life you've brought me nothing but happiness. I wish you all the belly rubs on this special day.
 I remember the first time I brought you home, you were just a little ball of fur, look how much you've grown. I can't wait for many more happy years with you.
 Happy bithday my friend.
